<p>Tincture provides a set of predefined named colors for common use cases, plus convenience functions for creating grayscale colors.</p>

<h3>Predefined Colors</h3>

<p>All named colors are available as constants on the <code>Color</code> type:</p>

<pre><code class="language-lean">import Tincture
open Tincture (Color)

let bg := Color.black
let fg := Color.white
let error := Color.red
let success := Color.green
let link := Color.blue</code></pre>

