<h3>Grayscale Colors</h3>

<p>For grayscale colors, use the <code>gray</code> function or predefined grays:</p>

<pre><code class="language-lean">-- Create custom gray (0.0 = black, 1.0 = white)
let midGray := Color.gray 0.5

-- Predefined grays
let dark := Color.darkGray    -- 25% brightness
let light := Color.lightGray  -- 75% brightness</code></pre>

